item.title: Normal Help :D
item.dc:creator: @M00_M00_Pk M00 M00 Pk
item.description:
@M00_M00_Pk wrote:

In my eyes, 508 is the biggest pile of crap thats hit this community.

Palidino shouldn’t have brought it here, as i myself dont want it.
Yes we can run 508 Clients with 317 Source Code (wich is what i do) but i think the 508 Cache coming out has just wrecked it for all of us.

317 Is win.
Lol.

We don’t really need this, and seeing as Palidino is from some other network, we should’ve just kept ourselves to ourselves, and waited for a person from our community to come and do this.
I object to 508.

But yeah i heard that there isn’t client.java, or anything from 317+ But the concept inside the files is the same, and uses Java language, just Google and you’ll find out how to edit it.
